Title: Sexmission
Writer: Juliusz Machulski (screenplay), Pavel Hajný (in collaboration with), Jolanta Hartwig (in collaboration with)
Actors: Wieslaw Michnikowski, Jerzy Stuhr, Olgierd Lukaszewicz, Dorota Stalinska
Plot: Two scientists are placed in hibernation and should be awaken after three years. But when they wake up, it turns out that it has been fifty years, and they are the only two males in a new, underground society composed exclusively of women.
